---
// Requested-songs card — lists pending requests that haven't yet shown up in
// now_playing or song_history. AzuraCast's actual request queue is behind
// auth, so the shared `efm-requests` service (Caddy-proxied at /requests/*)
// owns the canonical cross-visitor list; nowplaying.ts fetches + prunes it on
// every poll. The card hides itself when there's nothing pending so it
// doesn't take up sidebar real estate for free.
---

<section id="req-pending-section" class="hidden efm-sidebar-section">
  <div class="card !py-3 efm-sidebar-card">
    <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-1 lg:mb-2 shrink-0">
      <h2 class="text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-cream/65">Requested Songs</h2>
      <span id="req-pending-count" class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider text-sunburst"></span>
    </div>
    <ul id="req-pending-list" class="divide-y divide-cream/5 efm-sidebar-scroll"></ul>
  </div>
</section>
